channel.title: Run error help!
channel.description:
[code]The Lost Universe is Online Server is already in use. Starting Web Server at 0.0.0.0:8080 Exception in thread "main" java.lang.ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException: 3 at NPCHandler.loadNPCDrops(NPCHandler.java:2043) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:547) at server.main(server.java:115) [/code]
What's this mean or is it an error at all?
